              "displayName": "Konstantinos Karanasos",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "The idea is to add container tags whenever a container gets allocated or its execution finishes.\nGiven that only specific containers will have tags (especially those corresponding to long-running applications for which constraints will be useful), I don't think the load will be too much.\nBut if we see that it is, we can think of further optimizations.",
